      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REGAL SAINT (6) has a strong record here with five wins and two placings from eight starts. Hit the frame latest (19.84) when second at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5. With a clean break looks hard to beat. RAFFA (2) is a progressive type who recorded his 19th career win last time out (21.62) at Q Lakeside. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Can make it two on the bounce. WORKMAN LIKE (4) had some strong recent form but was below best last time when sixth (20.79) in a Mix 5 at Q Lakeside. Generally a safe beginner but buried in the ruck from a squeeze draw last time. Has a good record here at this journey. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Should be in this for a long way. PIPER BEACH (8) was a surprise last-start placegetter with solid claims again.",
